Title: Pagegen static site generator
Menu title: Home

.. sidebar:: Get Pagegen

	* `Download .deb </include/download/PAGEGEN_LATEST_DEB_URL>`_
	* `github.com <https://github.com/oliverfields/pagegen_v2>`_

Pagegen generates web sites from flat text files and directories, allowing you to manage your site from the command line.

* Pages are simple text files with `reStructured Text <http://docutils.sourceforge.net/rst.html>`_ markup
* Infinitely nested pages and generated navigational menu and breadcrumbs
* Web friendly URLs and sitemap
* Requires basic http server, no script or database support needed
* Run custom scripts during generation (e.g. automate FTP upload or CSS/JS compression)
* Template support